    "description": "Chef Floyd Cardoz&#39;s Pork Ribs Vindaloo recipe is the perfect dinner party dish. Cardoz created this juicy, saucy dish as an ode to his mother&#39;s pork vindaloo, using ribs instead of the more traditional shoulder.",
